│ right cols are key
│ merge ordering: +"(x=x)"
│
├── • scan
│     columns: (x, y)
│     ordering: +x
│     estimated row count: 1,000 (missing stats)
│     table: a@a_pkey
│     spans: FULL SCAN
│
└── • scan
      columns: (x)
      ordering: +x
      estimated row count: 1,000 (missing stats)
      table: b@b_pkey
      spans: FULL SCAN

